snippet.title: PAYDAY 2: John Wick Weapon Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Assassinating a target can be done in as many ways as imaginable, but when efficiency and precision are key the assassin need some tools of the trade. Guns, when used right, can yield the best desired results for the professional killer.

And this pack has one for every occasion...

Check out the website here: http://www.overkillsoftware.com/games/jwweaponpack/

The John Wick Weapon Pack DLC is released on Thursday 20th October for 4.99$ on Steam!
